	<h3>Concept</h3>
	<p>Inspired by work from interactive artists <a href="http://www.camilleutterback.com" rel="muse">Camille Utterback</a>, <a href="http://snibbe.com" rel="muse">Scott Snibbe</a> and <a href="http://number27.org" rel="muse">Jonathan Harris</a>, colleague <a href="http://tonydewan.com" rel="friend met colleague">Tony Dewan</a> and I designed an interactive art installa&shy;tion to inspire people to publicly behave in untraditional ways and interact with others they normally wouldn't.</p>
